cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper is focused on software security models and methods. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as the paper discusses the use of machine learning methods for discovering user expectations and setting security policy. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the changes in software over time and the need to revisit core security concepts. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses methods for efficient and detailed software monitoring and learning detailed software statistics.
